    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. So when you say \"restrained\" and \"not distracting,\" are you suggesting that certain cultural styles—like very voluminous natural hair or more vibrant traditional headwear—might actually be seen as less professional or authoritative compared to more standard Western styles? Like, is there a risk they'll be viewed as less serious if they don't conform to that polished, minimal look you mentioned earlier?",
